ch.bfh.ti.ostes2.gossip

Class LogRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.bfh.ti.ostes2.gossip.LogRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<LogRecord>

    public class LogRecord
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<LogRecord>
    This class represents a single record within the update-log of a ReplicationManager. It contains references to the ReplicationManager which stored the record, the time stamp of the ReplicationManager during the storing as well as message of the record itself. The class implements Comparable and overrides the compareTo() method allowing the comparison of log records.

    sosterwalder
